==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Slothful
<hw>Sloth"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Addicted to sloth;
inactive; sluggish; lazy; indolent; idle.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He also that is <qex>slothful</qex> in his work is brother to him
that is a great waster.</q> <rj><qau>Prov. xviii. 9.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Sloth"ful*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Sloth"ful*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Slothhound</ent>⟦br⟧
